Welcome to TRLib's documentation!
=================================

TRLib is a library that provides various methods related to the `trust region subproblem <https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trust-Region-Verfahren#Bemerkung_zur_L.C3.B6sung_des_quadratischen_Problems>`_ and in particular implements the Generalized Lanczos Method [Gould1999]_ for iterative solution of the trust region subproblem:

A detailed description of the problem and the method as well as the implementation can be found in [Lenders2016]_.

